<p class="ql-align-center">黄龙县人民政府副县长卢淑云致欢迎词</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201018/658e06a5c09a41509fdf12e92dd75d42.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">运动员代表宣誓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201018/d4df4fee948b4014bb78b9a88cf233a8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">裁判员代表宣誓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201018/5458476760c94857aa52a3a2decdac17.png" max-width="600" /></p>
